name: EYE AMULET WALLPAPER
description:
Eyes follow mole and blink randomly. Also, blink when poked. 

“Though often dubbed as ‘the evil eye’, the ocular amulet is actually the charm meant to ward off the true evil eye: a curse transmitted through a malicious glare, usually one inspired by envy.”

Animation, variable dimensions, generative, interactive - p5.js, HTML, CSS
Artist: Aleksandra Jovanic / @aleksandrajovanic  — September 2021
